            <textarea
              id="content"
              name="content"
              value={formData.content}
              onChange={handleInputChange}
              placeholder="Start writing your Istanbul story here...

Tell us about:
‚Ä¢ The places you visited and what made them special
‚Ä¢ Local food you tried and restaurants you'd recommend  
‚Ä¢ Cultural experiences and hidden gems you discovered
‚Ä¢ Practical tips for other travelers
